## StackLayer enum

The stack layer in which the log event occurred, i.e. which module caused the [ILogEvent](./jabra-js.ilogevent.md)<!-- -->.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare enum StackLayer 
```

## Enumeration Members

|  Member | Value | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  CHROME\_EXTENSION | <code>&quot;chrome-extension&quot;</code> | The log event was triggered by the Chrome extension. |
|  JS\_LIB | <code>&quot;js-lib&quot;</code> | The log event was triggered by the JavaScript SDK. |
|  NATIVE\_CONSOLE | <code>&quot;native-console&quot;</code> | The log event was triggered by the native console app (i.e. the low level USB HID layer). |
